                        <interp inst="t18470705-name-380" type="given" value="MARY"></interp>MARY SIMMONS.</persName>
                  </hi> I deal with Mr. Ormston for butter—on the 12th of June I paid the prisoner 10<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 4<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., for his master.</p>
